casebody.data:
James H. LACY
v.
UNITED STATES No. 19-6832 Supreme Court of the United States. February 24, 2020

The petition for writ of certiorari is denied.

Justice Sotomayor, with whom Justice Ginsburg joins, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States, 586 U. S. ---- (2018) ( Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
